sellerCard.description: Hello, I'm Khanwaiz Qureshi, a professional AI developer and full-stack developer from Pakistan with 5 years of dedicated experience in the field. I bring a blend of technical skill and creativity, consistently meeting project objectives on time. My expertise spans across website design, application development, and the integration of advanced AI functionalities. I am committed to fostering positive relationships with clients, management, and colleagues alike, and delivering solutions that align with both strategic goals and technical standards.

reviews.comment: Khan's team is professional. He is super busy but it's still better to have Zoom meetings with him & his team, otherwise some misunderstanding might happen. After the meeting, things went smoothly. Thanks!

I had the pleasure of working with this development team on a web app for my project, and I am thoroughly impressed with the results. From the very beginning, their professionalism and dedication were evident. They took the time to understand the unique needs of my project and provided insightful suggestions to improve the overall functionality and design.

The team was highly communicative, keeping me informed throughout the entire development process. They were quick to respond to any questions or concerns and ensured that any changes were implemented efficiently. The final product exceeded my expectations in both design and performance. The web app is user-friendly, visually appealing, and functions flawlessly across all devices.

Overall, I couldn’t be happier with the work they did. Their expertise and attention to detail have made a significant impact on the success of my project, and I would not hesitate to work with them again in the future. Highly recommended!

Very VERY satisfied with this delivery. I was quite honestly not expecting much and was kind of testing it because it was $450 but I was blown out of the water with the results. Khan is very professional and understanding and delivered everything he promised and more.

Khan truly impressed with his CODE EXPERTISE in AI Development, delivering top-quality results! 😊 Plus, his quick responsiveness and timely delivery made working with him a smooth and enjoyable experience. Highly recommend!
Very Good work, khan helps to make my dream app.
